    "summary": "Welcome to my LinkedIn profile! Beneath a brief introduction to Mazars and myself. Please contact me by e-mail if you like to know more on what we can mean for your organization: nancy.bergmans@mazars.nl\n\nMazars is one of the leading audit, advisory and tax firms in the Netherlands. We have a dynamic national practice backed up by our unique, international partnership - local roots with a global reach. Whilst we take a proactive, innovative approach to our clients\u2019 issues, we never forget the importance of personal attention. Mazars offers a wide range of services to entrepreneurial and owner-managed businesses, listed companies and wealthy individuals.\n\nI am working as an international tax partner at Mazars, providing tax advisory services. Mainly in an international, corporate and private equity environment. \n\nMy own specialisms are corporate tax and dividend withholding tax related, but in my work I also focus on identifying possible issues and opportunities for our clients on other tax areas like for example VAT, wage tax and global mobility by involving the specialists on these areas within Mazars. \n\nFurthermore I am helping our clients with their transfer pricing and CbCR compliance, working together with our TP specialists. \n\nUnderstanding my clients organization is an important pilar in my work to be able to identify opportunities and recognize potential risks. \n\nSpecialisations: \nCorporate Taxation\nNational and international\nInnovation \n\n.",
